- [ ] Add missing states (hover, focus, disabled, error)

**Week 6-7: Build Missing Components**
- [ ] Tabs component
- [ ] Accordion component
- [ ] Toast/Notification
- [ ] Empty states
- [ ] Loading states
- [ ] Pagination
- [ ] Breadcrumbs
