- [ ] Data display patterns (tables, lists, cards)
- [ ] Navigation patterns (sidebar, header, breadcrumbs)
- [ ] Modal patterns (confirmation, forms, detail views)

**Week 9-10: Documentation**
- [ ] Token documentation (when to use what)
- [ ] Component usage guidelines
- [ ] Accessibility guidelines
