- [ ] Update components to use new system

**Week 12: Training & Rollout**
- [ ] Designer training sessions
- [ ] Developer training sessions
- [ ] Update design file structure
- [ ] Update codebase with new tokens
- [ ] Monitor adoption and gather feedback

