## TOKEN STRUCTURE RECOMMENDATIONS

```json
{
  "primitives": {
    "color": {
      "blue": { "50-900": "10 shades" },
      "gray": { "50-900": "10 shades" },
      "green": { "50-900": "10 shades" },
      "red": { "50-900": "10 shades" },
      "yellow": { "50-900": "10 shades" }
    },
    "spacing": [4, 8, 16, 24, 32, 48, 64, 96, 128],
    "typography": {
      "size": [12, 14, 16, 18, 20, 24, 30, 36, 48, 60],
      "weight": [400, 500, 600, 700],
      "lineHeight": [1.25, 1.5, 1.75]
    },
    "radius": [0, 2, 4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 9999],
    "shadow": ["none", "sm", "md", "lg", "xl", "2xl"]
  },
  "semantic": {
    "background": ["primary", "secondary", "tertiary", "elevated", "overlay"],
    "text": ["primary", "secondary", "tertiary", "disabled", "link", "inverse"],
    "border": ["default", "strong", "hover", "focus", "error"],
    "action": ["primary", "primary-hover", "secondary", "secondary-hover"],
    "feedback": ["success", "success-bg", "warning", "warning-bg", "error", "error-bg", "info", "info-bg"]
  },
  "component": {
    "button": { "variants": ["primary", "secondary", "ghost"], "properties": ["background", "text", "border", "spacing"] },
    "input": { "properties": ["background", "text", "border", "spacing", "height"] },
    "card": { "properties": ["background", "border", "spacing", "radius", "shadow"] },
    "...": "Additional components"
  }
}
```

---

## COMPONENT MIGRATION STRATEGY

### Approach: Gradual Migration
**Not: Big bang rewrite**
**But: Incremental adoption with both old and new coexisting**

**Step 1: Create new design system file (Week 1-3)**
**Step 2: Build new components alongside old ones (Week 4-7)**
**Step 3: Document which screens use old vs new (Week 8)**
**Step 4: Migrate high-priority screens first (Week 11)**
**Step 5: Deprecate old components when 80% migrated (Week 12+)**

### Migration Mapping
```
Old Component ‚Üí New Component
Button_v1 (hard-coded #3B82F6) ‚Üí Button (uses component/button/primary/background/default)
Button_Blue ‚Üí Button variant="primary"
Button_Gray ‚Üí Button variant="secondary"
Button_Outline ‚Üí Button variant="ghost"

Input_Standard ‚Üí Input
Input_Error ‚Üí Input state="error"
Input_Disabled ‚Üí Input state="disabled"

Card_White ‚Üí Card
Card_Gray ‚Üí Card variant="secondary"
...
```

