## TIMELINE ESTIMATE

**Total Duration: 12 weeks**
**Team Required:**
- 1 Design System Lead (full-time)
- 2 Product Designers (50% time)
- 1 Frontend Engineer (full-time)
- 1 QA/Accessibility Specialist (25% time)

**Milestones:**
- Week 3: Token foundation complete ‚úì
- Week 7: All components tokenized and built ‚úì
- Week 10: Documentation complete ‚úì
- Week 12: Migration complete, system adopted ‚úì

**Risk Factors:**
‚ö†Ô∏è Team availability (holidays, other projects)
‚ö†Ô∏è Scope creep (new component requests)
‚ö†Ô∏è Migration complexity (legacy code issues)
‚ö†Ô∏è Adoption resistance (designers prefer old workflow)

**Mitigation:**
‚Üí Lock scope after Phase 1
‚Üí Create clear migration guide
‚Üí Weekly check-ins with stakeholders
‚Üí Celebrate early wins to build momentum

