## Quick Reference: When to Use AI Augmentation

| Task | Complexity | AI Value | Best Approach |
|------|-----------|----------|---------------|
| Analyze existing designs | ‚≠ê | High | Upload screenshots, ask for pattern identification |
| Complete color/spacing scales | ‚≠ê‚≠ê | Very High | Provide base values, LLM generates full scales |
| Create semantic tokens | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | High | Give primitives + context, LLM maps purposes |
| Component tokenization | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | Medium | Show components, LLM extracts token needs |
| Full system audit | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | Very High | Share Figma via MCP, request comprehensive audit |
| Gap identification | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | Very High | LLM compares your system to best practices |
| Accessibility validation | ‚≠ê‚≠ê | Very High | LLM checks contrast ratios, finds violations |
| Documentation generation | ‚≠ê‚≠ê | Medium | LLM writes usage guidelines from structure |
| Migration planning | ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê | High | LLM creates step-by-step migration strategy |

